    "description": "Taihei Machinery Works, Limited engages in the manufacture and sale of plywood machinery, woodworking machinery, and building materials for home applications in Japan. It operates through three segments: Plywood Machinery Business, Woodworking Machinery Business, and Housing Construction Materials Business. The company offers artesa, dryer, and horizontal hot press products, including Knife Grinder ARTESA I V94-AC and Knife Honer ARTESA II V95-AC; Roll Jet Dryer/SRJ-125; Type VF-5(4) Vacuum Pre-feeder; Horizontal Hot Press/P25-AB; and Automatic Infeed Device IRETARO/P91-AB. It also provides T-Scanner DX, which measures the condition of wood by scanning it with a laser camera, and extracts defects, such as its shape, knots, and insect bite; and finger jointing system. In addition, the company manufactures underfeed chipper, rapier, and shak racer. Further, it sells and renovates custom-built house; and sells wooden building materials for construction. Taihei Machinery Works, Limited was incorporated in 1925 and is headquartered in Komaki, Japan."
